OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,FA shortage of UK spaces means more
OL,7,Fthan a dozen prisoners in Jersey
OL,8,Fcannot transfer back to their home
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,FUnder the Repatriation of Prisoners
OL,12,F(Jersey) Law 2012, prisoners may be
OL,13,Ftransferred to the UK to serve their
OL,14,Fsentences if they are citizens there.
OL,16,FHowever, the States of Jersey Prison
OL,17,FService says 13 prisoners are still
OL,18,Fwaiting to be transferred to the UK to
OL,19,Fserve their sentences.
