OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,FOn average, the La Moye prison aims to
OL,7,Fsend one prisoner a month to the UK,
OL,8,Fbut only two have been transferred
OL,9,Fthis year.
OL,11,FGuernsey Prison has also revealed they
OL,12,Fare affected by the same restrictions,
OL,13,Fwith six prisoners currently unable to
OL,14,Ftransfer back to the UK.
OL,16,FA statement from the island's prison
OL,17,Fservice said: "Those on the transfer
OL,18,Fwaiting list face challenges in
OL,19,Fmaintaining family contact through in-
OL,20,Fperson visits.
