OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,F"Additionally, prisoners who cannot be
OL,7,Ftransferred may experience limited
OL,8,Faccess to resettlement and early
OL,9,Frelease opportunities available in the
OL,10,FUK, which would affect their
OL,11,Frehabilitation and reintegration
OL,12,Fprospects."
OL,14,FJersey's HMP La Moye currently houses
OL,15,Faround 140 prisoners, with a capacity
OL,16,Ffor up to 200, according to the prison
OL,17,Fservice's latest Annual Report.
OL,19,FHowever, the prison service says the
OL,20,Ftransfer stop will not directly affect
OL,21,Ftheir capacity.
