OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,FIn July, the UK parliament approved
OL,7,Flegal changes to make it easier for
OL,8,Fprisoners serving fixed sentences to
OL,9,Fbe released into the community on
OL,10,Flicence to free up more prison space.
OL,12,FUnder the previous law, offenders
OL,13,Fserving these fixed sentences were
OL,14,Fusually released from prison
OL,15,Fautomatically after serving half of
OL,16,Ftheir sentence.
OL,18,FThe UK government has now introduced
OL,19,Flegislation which allows these
OL,20,Fprisoners to be released on licence
OL,21,Fafter serving 40% of their sentence.
