OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,FThe hope is that this will reduce
OL,7,Fpressures on UK prisons nearing
OL,8,Fmaximum capacity.
OL,10,FThose serving sentences for certain
OL,11,Fsexual, violent, domestic abuse,
OL,12,Fterrorism and national security
OL,13,Foffences are excluded from these
OL,14,Fchanges to the law.
OL,16,FRob Preece, Communications Manager for
OL,17,FThe Howard League for Penal Reform,
OL,18,Fthe world's oldest prison charity,
OL,19,Fsays the "desperate" situation will
OL,20,Fdetrimentally affect prisoners.
