OL,3,CLack of UK prison spaces leaves
OL,4,Coffenders stuck out the country
OL,6,FHe explains: "It simply can't be right
OL,7,Fthat people are being held in prisons
OL,8,Fa long way from home without access to
OL,9,Ffamily and friends who might help them
OL,10,Fmove on from crime.
OL,12,F"Wherever possible you want people to
OL,13,Fbe serving their sentences close to
OL,14,Fthe people who care for them.
OL,16,F"While people may be fortunate enough
OL,17,Ffor people to come to Jersey to see
OL,18,Fthem, for many people that won't be an
OL,19,Foption so it's obviously an
OL,20,Fundesirable situation.
