OL,6,F"Hopefully the measures that the
OL,7,FGovernment are taking in the UK will
OL,8,Fensure that some people can be moved
OL,9,Fback quickly but the fact they can't
OL,10,Fat the moment just reflects how
OL,11,Fserious the situation is."
